===Adverb===
'''idcircō'''

# on that account
# for this reason, for that reason, for that purpose
#:''Lēgum dēnique idcircō omnēs servī sūmus, ut līberī esse possīmus'': Of the laws finally for this reason we are all slaves, that we may be free. (Cicero)

